{"about_the_game":"Step into the boots of a hardened bounty hunter in this third-person shooter set in a gritty, unforgiving Western world. As you navigate treacherous landscapes, from sun-scorched deserts to dense forests, you'll track down notorious outlaws with deadly reputations. Your story begins with the hunt for Prickly Pete, a cunning and ruthless target whose capture could set you up for life\u2014or end it. The game is a high-stakes journey of survival, skill, and the relentless pursuit of justice, where every decision could be your last.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Game Features: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 3D Third person shooter set in a western environment!<br></li><li> Story-driven gameplay!<br></li><li> Hunt bounties to gather the spell's missing pieces and summon the devil!<br></li><li> Fight with the four elements to take down bounties and their goons!<br></li><li> Upgrade your gun to get stronger!<br></li><li> Save your wife from the hands of The Devil!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723840146","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004310/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1723840146","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004310/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723840146","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004310/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723840146","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Step into the boots of a hardened bounty hunter in this third-person shooter set in a gritty, unforgiving Western world. As you navigate treacherous landscapes, from sun-scorched deserts to dense forests, you'll track down notorious outlaws with deadly reputations. Your story begins with the hunt for Prickly Pete, a